review: this is a very nice cover i have a tyndale life application study bible it fit perfectly and had room for a 5 x 7 spiral note book the price was great too

fits a macarthur study bible great it just has about an inch extra of vertical space side to side is about perfect interior pockets are nice and there is a bit of extra depth to use them it looks really nice and has kept my bible from getting beat up with daily travel in a backpack highly recommend
